{
  "texts": [
    "Citation Reward Given a query x ∈ D and a response y ∼ π θ (•|x), we evaluate citations with respect to a citation store S = {(i, s i)} mapping citation IDs i to snippets s i.",
    "We first extract a set of claims from y,",
    "with an associated (possibly empty) set of cited IDs for each claim,",
    "Citation-format reward.",
    "We reward valid citations by the fraction that resolve in S: Average F1."
  ]
